NOTICE TO DEFENDANT:

Pursuant to MCR 2.003(D)(1), this Motion for Disqualification will be heard and decided by the Chief Judge of the Muskegon County Circuit Court, not by Judge Jenny L. McNeill.

You have the right to file a response to this Motion. Your response must be filed within the time period allowed by court rules and served on all parties.

The hearing on this Motion will be scheduled by the Chief Judge. You will receive notice of the hearing date, time, and location.

If you disagree with the Motion for Disqualification, you should file a written response explaining your position and serve copies on all parties.

